              <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
            </span>
            Same-Day Sports Clearance
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.05]">
            Sports Physicals & <span class="text-blue-600">Return-to-Play Assessments</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-4">
            Get cleared for the season—or cleared to return after injury—quickly and confidently at Instant Orthopedic Care. We provide comprehensive sports physicals and structured return-to-play assessments for athletes of all ages, including youth, high school, college, and adult recreational sports.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
            Our orthopedic-trained providers evaluate overall musculoskeletal health, mobility, strength, previous injuries, and readiness for athletic participation—helping keep athletes safe on the field, court, slope, or track.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="https://pp-wfe-101.advancedmd.com/163338/onlineintake/demographic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/25 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">Check In Now</a>
