            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Whether your athlete needs preseason clearance for school sports, a club tryout, or an annual athletic physical, our team gets it done in a single same-day visit—including signed participation forms.
            </p>
          </div>

