    <!-- Return to Play -->
    <Section background="white" class="py-24">
      <Container>
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Return-to-Play Assessments</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4">Expert return-to-play evaluations</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Recovering from an injury and not sure if it's safe to return to sport? Returning too soon is one of the biggest causes of reinjury. Our return-to-play assessments help athletes safely transition back to competition after injury or surgery.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4">
              Our orthopedic-trained providers perform a detailed evaluation of healing, strength, stability, mobility, and functional performance before clearing an athlete to return to practice or competition.
            </p>
          </div>

